character.name: Lyra the Mentor
character.prompt: A young wise female scholar mentor with voluminous wavy lavender-purple hair pulled up into a high bun on top of her head. She has warm peachy-tan skin with golden undertones, large expressive dark eyes behind oversized round amber-brown glasses frames. She wears a deep navy blue scholar's robe with gold trim accents and slightly puffed layered shoulders. She holds an open leather-bound book with cream pages at chest level. Her expression is warm and approachable with a gentle knowing smile. The robe has visible fabric folds and draping.
